title: Cadillacs and Dinosaurs - The Second Cataclysm (DOS)
description:
NOTE: This is another better torrent of a previous one I up-loaded before. The game is in a compressed file for a smaller size, and the DOSBox guide is improved.


-------------


1995 DOS game "Cadillacs and Dinosaurs - The Second Cataclysm".

Released the year before on the Sega CD.

Rail-shooting sequel to the 1993 arcade beat'em up.

Manual PDF included, along with a simple guide for playing on DOSBox (DOS emulator).



7Zip compressed folder includes:
-The 3 game disc images (in .ISO format).
-Manual (.pdf).
-"To Use in DOSBox" guide (.txt).



Sorry but my upload speed is limited so please be patient and seed.

Thank you.
